<h1 style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: 400; color: #1a1a1a; margin: 0 0 30px 0;">Your password has been changed.</h1>

<p style="font-size: 15px; color: #666; margin: 0 0 25px 0;">
    Dear user <a href="mailto:<%= email %>" style="color: #00a6ff; text-decoration: none;"><%= email %></a>:
</p>

